{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01SUsR42bM51c1HvpYdv98bz","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_0141nWhgCP2YkL5ZCx6E4VGG","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"git add .github/workflows/release.yml && git commit -m \"$(cat <<'EOF'\nfeat(11d): restore .github/workflows/release.yml with 8-tier publish\n\nRestores the release workflow adapted to the 0.6.0 crate topology\n(7 publishable workspace crates + 2 binding packages) per\ndev/design/release.md § Tiered publish order. Triggered on `push` of\nv* tags or `workflow_dispatch` (dry-run rehearsal — see below).\n\nJob graph:\n\n  verify-release      preflight: actionlint + verify-release-gates.sh\n                      (tag↔Cargo.toml, set-version --check-files,\n                      HEAD-on-main, CHANGELOG section, crate publish\n                      metadata).\n  build-python        maturin matrix: linux x86_64/aarch64 (manylinux\n                      2_28), darwin x86_64/aarch64, win x86_64, py\n                      3.10/3.11/3.12. working-directory: src/python.\n  build-napi          napi-rs matrix: linux x86_64, darwin\n                      x86_64/aarch64, win x86_64. Uses `npm run\n                      build:native` so the napi.triples rename to\n                      fathomdb.<label>.node lives in one place.\n  build-rust          cargo build --release --workspace + cargo\n                      package --no-verify on the three leaf crates\n                      (fathomdb-embedder-api, fathomdb-schema,\n                      fathomdb-query). Dependents are not packaged\n                      here — see in-file comment for the rationale\n                      carried forward from the pre-0.6.0 source.\n  all-builds-passed   cross-ecosystem gate; every build must succeed\n                      before any publish runs.\n  publish-rust-t1..t7 strict 8-tier topological publish:\n                        T1 fathomdb-embedder-api  (leaf, Axis E)\n                        T2 fathomdb-schema        (leaf)\n                        T3 fathomdb-query         (leaf)\n                        T4 fathomdb-engine        (needs T1+T2+T3)\n                        T5 fathomdb-embedder      (needs T1, ordered\n                                                   on T4 for index-\n                                                   propagation cadence)\n                        T6 fathomdb               (facade, needs T4)\n                        T7 fathomdb-cli          (needs T6 per\n                                                   ADR-0.6.0-crate-\n                                                   topology 2026-05-11)\n                      Each tier sleeps 60s afterward for crates.io\n                      index propagation.\n  publish-pypi        Tier 8a, parallel with T5..T7 (gated on T4\n                      since PyPI wraps engine via PyO3).\n                      pypa/gh-action-pypi-publish with OIDC env.\n  publish-npm         Tier 8b, parallel with T5..T7 (gated on T4\n                      via napi-rs). npm OIDC trusted publishing\n                      via npx npm@latest publish --provenance\n                      --access public. working-directory: src/ts.\n  post-publish-smoke  AC-056 gate: 3-leg matrix runs scripts/release/\n                      smoke/smoke-{crates-cli,pypi-wheel,npm-package}.sh\n                      against the version-pinned published artifacts\n                      on fresh runners.\n  co-tagging-assert   AC-052 gate: scripts/release/assert-co-tagging.sh\n                      verifies the sibling triple is published.\n  github-release      AC-054 partial: only this job marks the release\n                      done. Requires post-publish-smoke +\n                      co-tagging-assert to pass, so a failed smoke\n                      leaves the release unmarked.\n\nworkflow_dispatch dry-run mode (Item 4):\n  inputs.dry_run defaults to true; when on:\n    * cargo publish steps use --dry-run.\n    * pypa/gh-action-pypi-publish points at https://test.pypi.org/\n      legacy/.\n    * npm publish runs with --dry-run.\n    * post-publish-smoke, co-tagging-assert, github-release are\n      skipped (they assume real publishes happened).\n    * verify-release-gates.sh is skipped (no v* tag context on a\n      dispatch trigger; the gate would always fail).\n\nAll third-party actions pinned to commit SHAs (H-5 convention,\nshared with ci.yml). actionlint .github/workflows/*.yml passes.\nEOF\n)\"","description":"Commit release.yml"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":919,"cache_read_input_tokens":177742,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":919},"output_tokens":56,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6c2ab885-f26f-4687-8076-7a046130c523","uuid":"39b47e24-86c5-4d31-9abb-cee7863d0cea"}
